heading: Plucked instrument octets.
general-note: Here are entered collections of octets not in a specific form or of a specific type for various combinations of eight plucked stringed instruments. Individual plucked instrument octets and collections not in a specific form or of a specific type for a single combination of instruments are entered under this heading followed by the instruments in alphabetical order..
Collections of compositions for eight plucked keyboard instruments are entered under. Keyboard instrument ensembles; Harpsichord ensembles, and similar headings..
